# Terraform state — never commit
**/.terraform/
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/terraform.tfstate.*.backup
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info

# Terraform variable files — never commit (use *.tfvars.example instead)
**/*.tfvars

# Lock files — committed for reproducible builds
# .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT ignored

# Crash logs
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Override files (local dev only)
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Plan output files
*.tfplan

# macOS
.DS_Store

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# Environment files — never commit
.env
*.env

# Claude Code session files
.claude/

# Plan output JSON (generated by terraform show -json)
**/plan.json

# Word documents — documentation is in docs/operations-guide.md
*.docx

# Internal scaffolding and build artifacts — not for external consumers
docs/scaffolding-notes.md
netskope-npa-self-service-demo-SPEC.md
